---
---

<section class="py-20 lg:py-28">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
    <div class="text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">
        Befintliga verktyg visar dig det här...
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-slate-400">
        Du ska inte behöva tolka screenshots. AI:n gör det åt dig.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2">
      <!-- Visualping side -->
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-red-500/20 bg-red-950/20 p-8">
        <div class="mb-4 flex items-center gap-2 text-red-400">
          <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">Andra verktyg</span>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-950 p-6">
          <!-- Simulated blurry diff -->
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="h-4 w-24 rounded bg-slate-700"></div>
              <div class="h-4 w-32 rounded bg-slate-700"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="relative">
              <div class="h-4 w-48 rounded bg-red-500/30"></div>
              <div class="absolute inset-0 h-4 w-48 rounded bg-red-500/20 blur-sm"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="h-4 w-36 rounded bg-slate-700"></div>
              <div class="h-4 w-20 rounded bg-slate-700"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="relative">
              <div class="h-4 w-40 rounded bg-red-500/30"></div>
              <div class="absolute inset-0 h-4 w-40 rounded bg-red-500/20 blur-sm"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="h-4 w-56 rounded bg-slate-700"></div>
            <div class="relative">
              <div class="h-4 w-44 rounded bg-red-500/30"></div>
              <div class="absolute inset-0 h-4 w-44 rounded bg-red-500/20 blur-sm"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-6 text-center text-sm italic text-slate-500">
            "Något har ändrats... men vad?"
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Pagewatch side -->
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-blue-500/20 bg-blue-950/20 p-8">
        <div class="mb-4 flex items-center gap-2 text-blue-400">
          <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">changebrief</span>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-950 p-6">
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="rounded-full bg-orange-500/20 px-2.5 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-orange-400">Importance: 8/10</span>
              <span class="text-xs text-slate-500">Idag 14:32</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-200">
              <strong class="text-white">Acme Corp</strong> tog bort <span class="rounded bg-red-500/20 px-1 text-red-300">"Gratis i 14 dagar"</span>-knappen och höjde Pro-priset från <span class="rounded bg-red-500/20 px-1 text-red-300">299 kr</span> till <span class="rounded bg-green-500/20 px-1 text-green-300">349 kr/månad</span>.
            </p>
            <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-200">
              Ny feature <span class="rounded bg-green-500/20 px-1 text-green-300">"AI Insights"</span> tillagd i Enterprise-planen.
            </p>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-6 text-center text-sm font-medium text-blue-400">
            Kristallklart. Direkt i Slack.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
